OL,3,C'A disgrace to the uniform': Ex-
OL,4,Cofficer jailed over murder probe calls
OL,6,FA former police officer, labelled by a
OL,7,Fjudge as a "disgrace to the uniform,"
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for a year for
OL,9,Fconspiring to pervert the course of
OL,10,Fjustice in relation to the sectarian
OL,11,Fmurder of a man in Portadown in 1997.
OL,13,FRobert Cecil Atkinson, 71 and of
OL,14,FBrownstone Road in Portadown, admitted
OL,15,Fconspiring to pervert the court of
OL,16,Fjustice in the investigation into the
OL,17,Fsectarian gang attack in the Co Armagh
OL,18,Ftown.
