OL,3,C'A disgrace to the uniform': Ex-
OL,4,Cofficer jailed over murder probe calls
OL,6,FMr Hamill was attacked by a loyalist
OL,7,Fmob after a night out. An RUC vehicle
OL,8,Fwith four officers inside was yards
OL,9,Faway, and this crew has previously
OL,10,Fbeen accused of failing to intervene.
OL,12,FThe young catholic man, a father of
OL,13,Fthree, succumbed to his injuries over
OL,14,Fa week later.
OL,16,FRetired RUC reservist Robert Cecil
OL,17,FAtkinson was one of those in the
OL,18,Fpolice vehicle that night.
