OL,3,C'A disgrace to the uniform': Ex-
OL,4,Cofficer jailed over murder probe calls
OL,6,FJailing Atkinson at Craigavon Crown
OL,7,FCourt, Judge Patrick Lynch KC told the
OL,8,Fpensioner: "It's a disgrace that you
OL,9,Fas a serving police officer should
OL,10,Fstoop so low as to deliberately
OL,11,Fmislead an investigation which you
OL,12,Fknew concerned a serious assault you
OL,13,Fhad witnessed."
